      <h1>CBDC Issuance System</h1>
      <p class="dp-cover-desc">
        The Issuance Tab is the central bank operator's interface for creating, authorising,
        and dispatching CBDC (CBDC Voucher in Bearer) batches. It covers the complete
        lifecycle from draft configuration through governance approval, note minting,
        vault encryption, and ownership transfer to commercial banks.
      </p>
